{
  "events": {
    "scene_1": {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "data": [
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "Awake, little godling. Does mortality feel as fragile as they say? A heartbeat, a breath... so easily snuffed.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Player",
          "line": "Where... am I? Who are you?",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Player.png",
          "right_sprite": "",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "A guardian of shadows. A savior. Your savior. Ask the better question: Why are you here?",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Player",
          "line": "I... don't remember. Why can't I remember...? What happened to me?",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Player.png",
          "right_sprite": "",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "Oh, you poor mortal. How could he have done this to you...? Don't worry, I'll give you the means for revenge.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Player",
          "line": "Can you stop speaking in riddles and tell me what is going on!",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Player.png",
          "right_sprite": "",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "You were just a child, so fueled with rage to gain power. Greedy. Bloodlusted. You screamed for Ares' blessings, and he gave themâ€”until you overreached. You thought yourself a god... until you fell.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "And oh, the blood price! A contract binding your soul to eternal servitude.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "*Grabs the player's hand, her grip icy*",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Player",
          "line": "Let go! I don't feel dead... or bound!",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Player.png",
          "right_sprite": "",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "Mortals never do. But you will. Unless you free yourself.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "*Tosses the player a sword wreathed in crimson war runes*",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "Take this blade. Sever your ties to Ares. Confront him on Olympus... and I will ensure your freedom.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Player",
          "line": "Was I really that stupid? To make such a trade...",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/NyxBackground.png",
          "left_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Player.png",
          "right_sprite": "",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "Nyx",
          "line": "Youth is folly. Now choose.",
          "background_sprite": "Assets/Backgrounds/PortalChoice.png",
          "left_sprite": "",
          "right_sprite": "Assets/Characters/Nyx.png",
          "audio": {
            "path": "",
            "loop": false
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}